---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - QuiKey">
    <section class="privacy-page">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 26, 2025</p>

                <h2>What QuiKey Does</h2>
                <p>
                    QuiKey is a macOS utility that adds actions to Finder (files/folders) and to selected text via the system Services menu.
                    It can send files to Gmail, upload to Google Drive, analyze files or selected text with AI, convert to PDF, compress media, and schedule backups.
                </p>

                <h2>Your Data</h2>
                <p>
                    QuiKey stores your settings <strong>locally on your Mac</strong>.
                    OAuth tokens and API keys are stored <strong>encrypted</strong>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    When you run an action, your files or selected text are sent directly to the relevant service
                    (Google, AI providers, etc.) — not through a QuiKey file-processing server.
                </p>

                <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>QuiKey connects to these services based on your actions:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Google</strong> (Gmail, Drive, Gemini) — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    <li><strong>OpenAI</strong> (ChatGPT) — <a href="https://openai.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenAI Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    <li><strong>Anthropic</strong> (Claude) — <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anthropic Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    <li><strong>OpenRouter</strong> (optional AI routing) — <a href="https://openrouter.ai/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenRouter Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    <li><strong>CloudConvert</strong> (optional PDF conversion fallback) — <a href="https://cloudconvert.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CloudConvert Privacy Policy</a></li>
                    <li><strong>Lemon Squeezy</strong> (payments) — <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lemon Squeezy Privacy Policy</a></li>
                </ul>
                <p>These services have their own privacy practices.</p>

                <h2>Analytics</h2>
                <p>
                    If enabled in Settings, QuiKey may send anonymous usage statistics (feature usage, success/failure rates) to help improve the app.
                    <strong>You can disable this</strong> at any time in Settings.
                </p>
                <p>We do not include your file contents in analytics events. If you use AI features, your prompt/file content is sent to the provider you selected.</p>

                <h2>Updates</h2>
                <p>We may update this policy. Check back occasionally.</p>

                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:support@quikey.app">support@quikey.app</a></p>
                <p>See also: <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .privacy-page {
        padding: 120px 0 60px;
        min-height: 80vh;
    }

    .privacy-content {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .privacy-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .privacy-content p {
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .privacy-content ul {
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-content li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-content a {
        color: #3b82f6;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .privacy-content a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .privacy-content strong {
        color: #1f2937;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .privacy-page {
            padding: 100px 0 40px;
        }

        .privacy-content h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
